          "reviewBody": "This school is sending the students during 9th standard who have studied from LKG to 8th stating the academic performance is not good.  Who is responsible for academic performance.  Both students and teachers.   While sending out without any hesitation on their future, where is the professionalism??  What is the pride to celebrate success with good students.",
