            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "A very bad school  which only gives encouragement to the Brahmin students and discourages Non-Brahmin students and tries to put down the Non-Brahmin students.  No encouragement for sports and Athletics. A school which has a casteist mentality.\n\nThe teachers here have no concept of empathy for the students. My nephew who studied here missed a test because his Grandfather passed away and one of the teachers punished him for missing the test and made a condescending remark about it eventhough he had a valid excuse for missing the test. A school which has no empathy for the students problems and the student's mental health.",
          "publisher": {
